<paragraph id="A5DFAA1BB1F0EBAC992C9FA596AECF9B" pageId="21" pageNumber="72">
= 
<taxonomicName id="8B78F4D58109466BC26CD1D503EC2A7C" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Zurus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zurus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="72" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="genus">Zurus</taxonomicName>
Heller, 1895: 5 (non Amyot, 1846). Type species: 
<taxonomicName id="E30DB7A0970F2026483F635CEA0A3926" authorityName="Heller" authorityYear="1895" class="Insecta" family="Curculionidae" genus="Zurus" higherTaxonomySource="CoL" kingdom="Animalia" lsidName="Zurus aurivillianus" order="Coleoptera" pageId="21" pageNumber="72" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="aurivillianus">Zurus aurivillianus</taxonomicName>
Heller, 1895 [by subsequent designation: 
<bibRefCitation id="8929B15FE581F82E04CF4EB63AB528BF" author="O'Brien, CW" journalOrPublisher="Memoirs of the American Entomological Institute" pageId="57" pageNumber="108" pagination="1 - 382" refId="B122" refString="O'Brien, CW, Wibmer, GJ, 1982. Annotated checklist of the weevils (Curculionidae sensu lato) of North America, Central America, and the West Indies (Coleoptera: Curculionidae). Memoirs of the American Entomological Institute 34: 1 - 382" title="Annotated checklist of the weevils (Curculionidae sensu lato) of North America, Central America, and the West Indies (Coleoptera: Curculionidae)." volume="34" year="1982">
<normalizedToken id="97AAFC932CDD726886DBA199CCFD9356" originalValue="O’Brien">O'Brien</normalizedToken>
and Wibmer 1982
</bibRefCitation>
: 8].
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="5BFF36012AD152227B980993B7EE532B" pageId="21" pageNumber="72">
